description:
In api-ref/source/servers-admin-action.inc, the following parameters' type should be 'object'.

* createBackup
* os-resetState

And there is a missing parameter in 'os-migrateLive' Action.
It is 'os-migrateLive'(object).
title: api-ref:  wrong parameter type and a missing parameter in servers-admin-action.inc
